      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable transportation, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. Priced fairly and represented honestly, it\u2019s a great chance to get into a car without spending a fortune. If you appreciate straightforward deals and good value, this one is worth a look.",
