    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with a dependable powertrain and plenty of life left for someone who wants an affordable daily, backup vehicle, or light project. Shows cosmetic wear consistent with age and use, but the drivetrain feels willing and the chassis remains serviceable. A good opportunity to get into a usable vehicle at a sensible price without paying for perfect cosmetics. Priced to move and well-suited for a hands-on owner who appreciates mechanical value.",
